node.text:
Hello my beautiful friends !!! I know getting a workout can be tough, especially when access to gyms are limited or just not an option. So I put together this quick workout routine you can do from the comfort of your home to keep your core nice and tight ! This workout and like all my workouts lol is powered by @redline_energy
Follow the ceo: @bangenergy.ceo
#bangenergy #redline #workout #preworkout #fitness #core #inspo #homeworkout #abs #energydrink

Since Instagram is mainly pictures, the occasional video post (usually one very long selfie video), and a few stories, I decided to do another Q and A video to help us all get better acquainted! 😄 In this video I answered the following questions:
1.Best Tulum Beach Club

3.Recommendations on how to grow instagram pages
4. Have I ever done yoga
5.Would I rather win 50k or my bff win 1 million
6.Biggest goal for this year
7.Am I going to practice law
8.Am I ready to take the bar
9.My weight and height
10.Where I stayed in Tulum, Mexico
11. What made me pursue a law degree
Thank you for tuning in!!! 
 
Beverage of choice (LIKE ALWAYS) @BANGENERGY RADICAL SKADATTLE

#bangenergy #energydrink #questions #answers  #vlog #qandA #tulum #fitness #law
